PN,39302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FMs Ghey previously said that during
OL,7,Fthe three years Brianna attended
OL,8,FBirchwood Community High School in
OL,9,FWarrington, there were 120
OL,10,Fsafeguarding logs and 116 behaviour
OL,11,Flogs around her phone use.
OL,13,FShe joined the Duke of Westminster
OL,14,FHugh Grosvenor and Cheshire Police and
OL,15,FCrime Commissioner Dan Price on a
OL,16,Fvisit to Sir William Stanier school in
OL,17,FCrewe, as it became one of the latest
OL,18,Fin Cheshire to introduce the signal-
OL,19,Fblocking pouches.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FMs Ghey said: "It's been really
OL,7,Femotional. It's been really lovely as
OL,8,Fwell."
OL,10,FShe has said her campaign for online
OL,11,Fsafety was "absolutely a legacy for
OL,12,FBrianna".
OL,14,FShe added: "All of the work I do, it's
OL,15,Fall based on my experience with
OL,16,FBrianna and my experience as a parent.
OL,18,F"When Brianna passed away I just knew
OL,19,Fthat it couldn't have been for
OL,20,Fnothing, we needed to make positive
OL,21,Fchange out of it."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FShe said she felt positive about
OL,7,Fspeculation that the Government is
OL,8,Fabout to announce a social media ban
OL,9,Ffor under-16s.
OL,11,FThree quarters of Cheshire's high
OL,12,Fschools have pledged to go phone-free
OL,13,Fusing the pouches, rather than an "out
OL,14,Fof sight" policy, from the start of
OL,15,Fthe next academic year.
OL,17,FThe pouches are now available to buy
OL,18,Ffrom as little as #3 per pupil on an
OL,19,Fonline buying portal, which has been
OL,20,Flaunched by Mr Price.
OL,26,@uD@cOUvD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FHe said: "The policy of out of sight
OL,7,Fand turning phones off just doesn't
OL,8,Fwork.
OL,10,F"Loads of schools that have introduced
OL,11,Fpouches had precisely that tough
OL,12,Fpolicy beforehand and they talk about
OL,13,Fthe significant change once they
OL,14,Fintroduce pouches.
OL,16,F"We need a technological solution to
OL,17,Fdevices that have been designed to be
OL,18,Faddictive."
OL,20,FYear 10 student Darryl said he
OL,21,Fwelcomed the new policy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FHe said: "I think it will help our
OL,7,Fstudents be more interactive and be
OL,8,Fmore vocal with each other and have
OL,9,Fless distractions in lessons."
OL,11,FThe Duke has made a personal donation
OL,12,Fof #250,000 along with #150,00 set
OL,13,Faside by the police and crime
OL,14,Fcommissioner over two years to support
OL,15,Fall of the state high schools in the
OL,16,Fcounty.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FThe Duke of Westminster, a close
OL,7,Ffriend of the Prince of Wales, said:
OL,8,F"We are seeing real, measurable
OL,9,Fimprovements in young people's
OL,10,Fwellbeing, focus and safety thanks to
OL,11,Fphone-free education.
OL,13,F"But perhaps the most powerful thing
OL,14,FI've heard, speaking to young people,
OL,15,Fis simply the relief of being able to
OL,16,Fswitch off during the school day, free
OL,17,Ffrom the constant pull of
OL,18,Fnotifications and the anxiety of
OL,19,Falways being contactable.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,F"Through my work with the Westminster
OL,7,FFoundation, I've seen how evidence-
OL,8,Fbased interventions can make a lasting
OL,9,Fdifference to young people's lives.
OL,11,F"What Dan Price and his team have
OL,12,Fbuilt here is something the whole
OL,13,Fcountry can benefit from.
OL,15,F"By creating this online portal,
OL,16,FCheshire is giving schools everywhere
OL,17,Fa simple, practical route to go phone-
OL,18,Ffree."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781168735
OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mother 'emotional' as
OL,4,Cschools stop students using phones
OL,6,FHeadteacher Elizabeth Robinson said:
OL,7,F"We see this as another positive step
OL,8,Fin helping pupils focus, learn and
OL,9,Fthrive.
OL,11,F"We are pleased that the vast majority
OL,12,Fof pupils, parents and carers have
OL,13,Ffully supported this approach and
OL,14,Frecognise the benefits it can bring.
OL,16,F"At Sir William Stanier school we are
OL,17,Fconfident that reducing mobile phone
OL,18,Fuse during the day will strengthen the
OL,19,Fpositive culture we are building and
OL,20,Fsupport pupils to focus, learn and
OL,21,Fachieve their best."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
